'''Ilew n Tmazɣa''' neɣ '''Ilew n Tefriqt ugafa''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Loxodonta africana pharaoensis''') d yiwet n [[tadfert|tedfert]] n [[ilew n imudaɣ]], akken daɣen i ttwalin kran [[amesnudran|imusnawen]] d akenn tadfert-a d tilellit ɣef tiyyad. Ilew-a yella yettidir deg yakk [[Tafriqt n Ugafa]] armi dayen [[angar|yenger]] di tallit n tnaya n [[Amenkud aṛuman|umenkud arumani]]. Iluten-a d wid-a isxedmen  [[Qerṭaj|iqertajen]] deg [[imsenɣiwen ipuniken]] mgal [[igen|ignan]] iṛumiyen.

== Aglam ==
[[Asugnalus]] aqerṭaj (am yidrimen n tallit nni) d akken ilew n tmazɣa yella meẓẓiy anda addud-is ar tuyat 2,5 m. Ma d imeẓẓaɣ-is meqqr-it, Ahat daɣen yella ameli ugar n tdefrin n iden ɣef wannect-a yezmer ad yili [[agrad|yettwagrad]] 

